@Node "Future Additions" "LinkZ88.guide/Future Additions"
@Toc "Main"

Future Additions
****************

   As I said in the introduction, I have no real plans for future
developments of LinkZ88. I think however the following might get
implemented:

   @{b}*@{ub} Printer pass through, allowing the Z88 to print on the Amiga's
     printer via LinkZ88.

   @{b}*@{ub} Utility programs to convert to / from Amiga and Z88 file formats.


@EndNode

